OL,6,FIn 2009 the Real IRA claimed
OL,7,Fresponsibility for the killing, and
OL,8,Fthe Spotlight programme was broadcast
OL,9,Fin September 2016 while a garda
OL,10,Finvestigation into the matter was
OL,11,Fongoing.
OL,13,FIn the programme, an anonymous source
OL,14,Fidentified as "Martin", who says he
OL,15,Fwas an informant for Special Branch
OL,16,Fwithin the IRA, claimed that the
OL,17,Fshooting was sanctioned by the
OL,18,Fpolitical and military leadership of
OL,19,Fthe IRA and that Mr Adams "gives the
OL,20,Ffinal say".
